{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1678-09e_386", "resp": "mercure"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "[Proposition pour construire des fictions sur l’origine de l’Horloge de Sable] *"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Extraordinaire du Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", quartier de juillet 1678 (tome III), p. 386-387."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "On a pris tant de plaisir à faire des Fictions sur cette origine des Mouches galantes, que je ne doute point qu’on ne se divertisse également à chercher celle de l’Horloge de Sable. La version que j’ay veu d’une Epigramme Latine, pourra servir d’idée à inventer quelque chose d’agreable sur ce sujet. La voicy."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "ALcippe dont le cœur fut autrefois si tendre,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Compte icy les Heures du Jour."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Il fut consumé de l’Amoureux"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Qui reduisit son corps en cendre."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Son continuel mouvement"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "Fait voir qu’on n’a jamais de repos en aimant."}]}]}]}